OL,7,FAn extremist group responsible for
OL,8,Fplanning what could have been "one of
OL,9,Fthe deadliest terrorist attacks in UK
OL,10,Fhistory" have been jailed for a total
OL,11,Fof 63 years.
OL,13,FWalid Saadaoui, 38, and Amar Hussein,
OL,14,F52, had a "visceral dislike" of Jewish
OL,15,Fpeople and wanted to kill as many as
OL,16,Fthey could in their Islamic State-
OL,17,Finspired gun attack in Greater
OL,18,FManchester.
