OL,3,CExtremists who planned 'one of the
OL,4,Cdeadliest terrorist attacks in UK'
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FTheir plan was to target a community
OL,8,Fgathering before moving on to a
OL,9,FBritish military base for a "last
OL,10,Fstand" where they sought a gunfight
OL,11,F"to the death".
OL,13,FBut the duo were brought down after an
OL,14,Fundercover operative posed as one of
OL,15,Fthem to gain their trust, tracking
OL,16,Ftheir every move for six months before
OL,17,Farmed officers swooped in to arrest
OL,18,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
