OL,4,Cdeadliest terrorist attacks in UK'
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"This is one of the biggest covert
OL,8,Fplots disruptions in the UK for a
OL,9,Fnumber of years," Assistant Chief
OL,10,FConstable Rob Potts, from Counter
OL,11,FTerrorism Policing North West said.
OL,13,F"The number of individuals that were
OL,14,Finvolved in this operation, and the
OL,15,Fpotential consequences had the
OL,16,Fsubjects been allowed to carry out
OL,17,Ftheir plan, are pretty unthinkable -
OL,18,Fcatastrophic."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
