OL,4,Cdeadliest terrorist attacks in UK'
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHe added: "With that level of weaponry
OL,8,Fand ammunition it could have been one
OL,9,Fof the deadliest terrorist attacks in
OL,10,FUK history."
OL,12,FMain instigator Saadaoui aimed to
OL,13,Fsmuggle four AK-47 assault rifles, two
OL,14,Fhandguns and 900 rounds of ammunition
OL,15,Finto the UK to carry out his attack.
OL,17,FMonths earlier the father-of-two,
OL,18,Foriginally from Tunisia, paid a
OL,19,Fdeposit for the weapons and believed
OL,20,Fhe had arranged for their importation
OL,21,Fwith a like-minded extremist.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
