OL,3,CExtremists who planned 'one of the
OL,4,Cdeadliest terrorist attacks in UK'
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FBut he was in fact the undercover
OL,8,Fofficer, referred to in court as
OL,9,FFarouk.
OL,11,FSaadaoui told Farouk he could
OL,12,Findependently obtain a firearm via
OL,13,FSweden and indicated he was looking to
OL,14,Fbring guns from eastern Europe.
OL,15,FSeparately he had bought an air weapon
OL,16,Fand had visited a shooting range.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
