OL,3,CExtremists who planned 'one of the
OL,4,Cdeadliest terrorist attacks in UK'
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FAs he arrived at a hotel car park in
OL,8,FBolton, on 8 May 2025, to collect some
OL,9,Fof the firearms he believed he had
OL,10,Fbought, counter terrorism police
OL,11,Fintervened - with more than 200
OL,12,Fofficers involved - and he was
OL,13,Farrested.
OL,15,FFollowing a 10-week trial, it took a
OL,16,Fjury at Preston Crown Court just two
OL,17,Fdays to find the two men guilty of
OL,18,Fplotting to carry out the attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
