OL,7,FDuring the trial Preston Crown Court
OL,8,Fheard Saadaoui hero-worshipped Islamic
OL,9,FState (IS) terrorist Abdelhamid
OL,10,FAbaaoud who orchestrated the 2015
OL,11,FParis terror attacks in which 130
OL,12,Fpeople were killed and hundreds more
OL,13,Finjured in gun attacks across the city.
OL,15,FHe came to the attention of
OL,16,Fauthorities after using 10 Facebook
OL,17,Faccounts, none of which were in his
OL,18,Fown name, to spread a torrent of
OL,19,FIslamic extremist views and praise
OL,20,FAbaaoud.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
