OL,4,Cdeadliest terrorist attacks in UK'
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FFarouk was then deployed to gain his
OL,8,Ftrust online and later in person.
OL,10,FSaadaoui, a former children's
OL,11,Fentertainer, used one of his fake
OL,12,Faccounts to join the Facebook group of
OL,13,Fthe Jewish Representative Council of
OL,14,FGreater Manchester which contained
OL,15,Fdetails of a "March Against
OL,16,FAntisemitism" held in the city centre
OL,17,Fon 21 January 2025 which thousands
OL,18,Fattended.
