OL,7,FDays later he told Farouk: "Here in
OL,8,FManchester, we have the biggest Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,F"God willing we will degrade and
OL,12,Fhumiliate them (in the worst way
OL,13,Fpossible), and hit them where it
OL,14,Fhurts."
OL,16,FSaadaoui recruited fellow IS
OL,17,Fsympathiser Hussein, a Kuwaiti
OL,18,Fnational, who worked and lived at a
OL,19,Ffurniture shop in Bolton, Greater
OL,20,FManchester, to assist his plans.
