OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe pair travelled to Dover, Kent, in
OL,8,FMarch 2024 to conduct hostile
OL,9,Freconnaissance on how a weapon could
OL,10,Fbe smuggled through the port without
OL,11,Fdetection.
OL,13,FOn his return, Saadaoui travelled to
OL,14,FPrestwich and Higher Broughton in
OL,15,Fnorth Manchester where he carried out
OL,16,Fsimilar surveillance on Jewish
OL,17,Fnurseries, schools, synagogues and
OL,18,Fshops.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
