OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA safe house was also secured in
OL,8,FBolton for the storage of the weapons
OL,9,Fas both men returned to Dover two
OL,10,Fmonths later where they believed they
OL,11,Fwere watching the firearms coming into
OL,12,Fthe country.
OL,14,FThe attack could have been 'the
OL,15,Fdeadliest terror attack' in UK history
OL,16,Fhad the operation not been thwarted,
OL,17,Faccording to one of the country's most
OL,18,Fsenior counter terrorism officers.
