OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FProsecutor Harpreet Sandhu KC told the
OL,8,Ftrial Walid Saadaoui 'hero-worshipped'
OL,9,Fthe mastermind of the 2015 terror
OL,10,Fattacks in Paris, Abdelhamid Abaaoud,
OL,11,Fa marauding gun massacre which left
OL,12,F130 dead and hundreds wounded.
OL,14,FThe trial at Preston Crown Court heard
OL,15,FTunisia-born holiday camp entertainer
OL,16,Fturned restaurateur Walid Saadaoui was
OL,17,Fan Islamic State fanatic, but his plot
OL,18,Fwas thwarted thanks to an undercover
OL,19,Foperative posing as a fellow IS
OL,20,Fenthusiast - named only 'Farouk'
OL,21,Fduring the trial.
